name: Free Harambe
description:
Free Harambe from all the obstacles on his course. Don't let him drown in the ocean. Don't let him hit any walls or bump into any trees. Just jump his way to freedom and collect as many coins along the way. The more coins the more characters you can unlock. Each locked characters come with increasing health and the real Harambe is almost immortal. Trees and walls won't stop him.

Enjoy playing this game and free Harambe!

Game Features:
• Beautiful images.
• Collect Coins
• Exciting, endless gameplay.
• Gamecenter leaderboard
• Unlock Adorable Characters
• Harambe
